The off ering of the Timnath Landing commercial/retail pad sites in Timnath,Colorado
presents an exceptional opportunity for retailers to secure a position in the booming Fort
Collins submarket. The site is strategically located on Harmony Road(County Road 5),among
thousands of existing and new home starts. The average household income is$109,104 within
a fi ve mile radius; residents are highly educated with 65.1 percent of the population holding
an associate’s degree or higher; and ready to spend with an average consumer household
budget of$91,955/year. The retail off ering is aptly positioned at the entrance to Timnath
Landing’s residential development,scheduled to break ground Q4 2018.
We are seeking quality retailers and restaurants to anchor this burgeoning development.

Located in the heart of Fort Collins’ historic Old Town the property is surrounded
by restaurants, breweries, outdoor activities, shopping and is within walking
distance of Colorado State University. A walking score of 96 and biking score of
100 makes it a convenient and desirable location for professionals and students
alike. In addition to an abundance of street parking surrounding the development,
the property is directly on the Max Transit Line providing reliable transportation
throughout Fort Collins.

Fort Collins submarket fundamentals are outstanding with 94.2% apartment
occupancy levels that are supported by the city’s annual growth rate of 1.5%. Key
employers include Otter Box, Colorado State University, UCHealth, Woodward
Inc, Madwire Media and Anheuser-Busch.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to present a re-development opportunity consisting of 32,600 SF
located at 121 W Olive Street and 120 W Magnolia Street in Old Town Fort Collins. The property consists of two lots and is well suited for apartment and/or mixed use
development. The site grants future users access to the best experience Fort
Collins has to offer. Developers can construct up to 79,000 SF on the site. The property is within the Transit-Oriented Development overlay creating a lower parking ratiowhich will allow more units to be constructed. The offering is the only Multi Family development site available for a fee interest in Old Town Fort Collins.
